  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Visit some of Europe's most iconic peaks on this popular Switzerland multi-centre holiday</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> means you get to experience the best of both worlds. Spend a couple of days exploring the sights of the Jungfrau region from Grindelwald before heading to the chocolate-box town of Zermatt, famous as the home of the Matterhorn.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1925pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options: </h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Flexible durations in each destination</li>
<li>Travel and change destination on a Wednesday, Friday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights or trains from the UK</li>
<li>2nd class train transfers from the airport to your hotel in Grindelwald, from your hotel in Grindelwald to your hotel in Zermatt and from your hotel in Zermatt to the airport (some changes of trains required, 1st class upgrade possible at extra cost)</li>
<li>Swiss Half Fare Card - worth over £100 – included as part of your rail tickets</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 4 nights in a Lifestyle Chic Room at Eiger Mountain &amp; Soul Resort, Grindelwald and 3 nights in a Classic Twin Room at Hotel Alex, Zermatt with train transfers between resorts, departing on the 7th June 25 from Manchester airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 21/11/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
